cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.GR 

This paper deals with deep reinforcement learning agents and their decision-making process, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also introduces a novel method for creating counterfactual states using generative deep learning architecture, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also evaluates the effectiveness of counterfactual states on human participants, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and graphics (cs.GR).
